State of North Carolina
v.
Timothy Wiley, Jr. No. 201P16 Supreme Court of North Carolina. August 18, 2016 Ms. Amy Kunstling Irene, Special Deputy Attorney General, Mr. Michael Bonfoey, for State of North Carolina. Ms. Anne M. Gomez, Assistant Appellate Defender, Mr. Timothy Wiley, Jr., for Wiley, Timothy (Jr.)

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 23rd of May 2016 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the Superior Court, Jackson County, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court of that County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 18th of August 2016."
